# Generated by `npm run wasm` (wasm-pack glue + the base64-embedded module).
# Baked fresh on install/build via the package's `prepare` and `build` scripts,
# so it is build output — not source — and is never committed. Building the
# package (or `npm install` at the repo root) requires the Rust toolchain plus
# wasm-pack to regenerate it.
/src/wasm/
